  "intent": "Prepare and execute a multi-mastermix PCR protocol with automated liquid handling. Mix PCR reagents (buffer, primers, dNTPs, MgCl2, polymerase) with water in falcon tubes to create up to 3 mastermixes with 10% excess volume. Distribute mastermix aliquots (reaction volume minus sample volume) to 96-well PCR plate wells, then add 1\u00b5L sample DNA to designated wells with specified replicates. Execute thermocycler program: initial denaturation at 98\u00b0C for 2 minutes, followed by 35 cycles of 95\u00b0C/30s, 60\u00b0C/30s, 72\u00b0C/30s, then final extension at 72\u00b0C for 5 minutes. Maintain reagents at 4\u00b0C throughout preparation.",
